# AgentCash — private agent guardrails (local only)

**Copy this file to `Private.md` at the repo root** and edit `Private.md`. The real `Private.md` is **gitignored** and never pushed to GitHub.  
**Do not put production secrets here** if you ever copy this file; use `.env.local` and Cloudflare/CI secret stores for keys.

